org.cds06.speleograph.data

Class SpeleoDataFileReader.DateInformation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cds06.speleograph.data.SpeleoDataFileReader.DateInformation
  • Enclosing class:
    SpeleoDataFileReader

    public static class SpeleoDataFileReader.DateInformation
extends Object
    Store date-column link information for a file.

    Each column can be link to a java date format scheme. When we read an entry, we join all columns for date and all date formats and ask to Java to parse it. If we got an error on parse, just return the actual date.
